OL,5, The government has warned energy firms 
OL,6, not to hike customers' direct debit    
OL,7, payments when households are making    
OL,8, "huge efforts" to cut usage.           
OL,10,FThe business secretary has written to  
OL,11,Fsuppliers asking them to ensure bills  
OL,12,Fshow what homes are actually using, as 
OL,13,Fopposed to overcharging on estimates.  
OL,15,FGrant Shapps said he was concerned by  
OL,16,Freports direct debits are rising as    
OL,17,Fpeople take steps to cut energy bills. 
OL,19,FRegulator Ofgem has been asked to look 
OL,20,Fat making billing "more responsive".   
